title: How New York City Can Make Housing More Affordable
descriptions: With few vacancies, rents in New York City have become some of the most unaffordable in the world. People with subsidized housing vouchers often have nowhere to go to use them. Housing production is a critical part of any solution to housing affordabilityâ€”in New York and elsewhere.
